Title: Service Discovery: Permissions for moving services can be assigned to user role
Level: 1
Component: wato
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.5.0i4
Date: 1522741446
Class: feature

The service discovery dialog has different action
buttons within the service tables
<ul>
<li>Undecided services</li>
<li>Monitored services</li>
<li>Disabled services</li>
<li>Vanished services</li>
</ul>

These actions are
<ul>
<li>Move to undecided services</li>
<li>Move to monitored services</li>
<li>Move to Disabled services</li>
<li>Remove services</li>
</ul>

For each action permissions can be set below
{{WATO - Check_MK's Web Administration Tool}}
in the user roles.
